they have said that the items you have enquired about are very unlikely =
to be affected by the fire given their location with respect to the =
proximity of the fire. I do understand that you would like to be 100% =
certain that the lithium batteries in these items have not been affected =
from the fire. The standard process in this situation is that you can =
undertake any testing of any of your items which you wish to, to obtain =
test results or a report which your insurer can consider for inclusion =
in your claims. If the test results prove any damage or loss to these =
items from the fire =E2=80=93 then your insurer will consider them =
within your claim.
