>>> Kindly confirm in writing:
>>> When I will receive your written responses and the meeting date =
(with agenda).
>>> My inclusion in all future briefings/inspections and provision of =
prior notes/photos.
>>> The testing plan (roof/eaves, cavities, HVAC/heat pumps & gas =
heating, electrical, gas, water, moisture/corrosion, IAQ) with labs, =
pass criteria, and dates.
>>> A revised scope that is test-led and targets as-new outcomes (not =
cosmetic sealing).
>>> The Council/AC2213 path and CPEng engagement (consent or written =
