style=3D"font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"mso-list:l9 level1 lfo12"><span =
style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:Helvetica">A proposed timeline for =
the next phases: removal, scoping, approvals, tendering, and =
