iv><div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I felt =
that the meeting was very productive and positive as we all discussed =
the next steps and have agreed on the claim=E2=80=99s progression =
process moving forward.</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div><div><d=
iv><div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I would =
like to re-confirm the next steps we agreed to in writing, and share =
with all as below:</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div><div><d=
iv><div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div></div><ol =
