class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo10"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Restore to attend site as =
soon as possible and complete the process of assessing and cataloging =
the contents for the response of the contents claim. After assessment =
the contents which are categorised as a total loss will be removed from =
site.</span><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo10"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Restore to strip out the =
property of any fire or smoke damaged linings or other non-structural =
items. This will enable a clear and clean structural assessment to be =
undertaken, from which we will produce a scope of works for the repairs =
required.</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo10"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Once we have a scope of works =
