style=3D"margin-top: 5pt; margin-bottom: 5pt;"><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">On 12 Sep 2025, =
at 5:37<span style=3D"font-family: Arial, =
sans-serif;">=E2=80=AF</span>PM,<span =
class=3D"Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a =
href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com" style=3D"color: blue; =
