making.<span style=3D"font-size: =
10pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></li></ol><p><span style=3D"font-size: 9pt; =
font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;">Could you please confirm which of =
these approaches Tower is prepared to adopt, so that I am not unfairly =
disadvantaged by circumstances outside my =
control?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><b><span style=3D"font-size: 9pt; =
